<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For this grand tournament, participants will be ranked purely according to their total cumulative purchase volume of GWEI tokens during the promotion periods. Selling volume is completely excluded. The </span><b>top 2,000 users</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> by buy volume in each respective period will share the 680,000 GWEI token pool equally.</span></p>
<h3><b>The Early Bird Boost Multiplier</b></h3>
