<h3><b>The Rising Trader Boost Multiplier</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Are you a casual trader or a newcomer to the Alpha ecosystem? Binance has built-in protection to make sure high-frequency institutional players don&#8217;t hog the leaderboards. If you have won rewards in </span><b>fewer than 5</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> previous Binance Wallet Alpha trading competitions as of three days before the promotion starts, you qualify as a </span><b>Rising Trader</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Eligible Rising Traders receive an extra </span><b>1.2x boost multiplier</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> on their actual trading volume, applied up to a maximum trading cap of 5,000 USDT equivalent.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">When both multipliers apply, your complete scored weight is calculated using this robust formula:</span></p>
